  "label": "Morcant Thryss",
  "description": "This individual is an ork corpse animated by crude necromantic energies, its dark_green skin shrunken tight over protruding bone. Orange eyes burn steadily within deep sockets, and a green-tinted jaw bears broken tusk-stumps that never fully close. Black hair hangs in stiff, patchy cords across a skull ridged with old fractures and impact dents. The hands remain heavy and swollen, ending in chipped nails that function as blunt, enduring tools.",
